Parliament elections, with only 182 parishes left to be counted, 
show the Socialist Party leads with 34.7 percent, followed 
closely by the Social Democratic Party with 34.4 percent, then 
the Centrists with 12.5 percent, and the Communist-Greens 
coalition with 11.2 percent. 

