<H3> <TI>   Spokesman Avoids Comment </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Spokesman Avoids Comment </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1106111794 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1030 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1106111794 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
