BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] Eleven terrorists have been killed in clashes with 
the security forces in Sirnak, Bingol, Batman, Diyarbakir and 
Elazig. Twelve persons abetting the terrorists have been 
captured in Bitlis. 
  One terrorist involved in many incidents of murder and arson 
in Igdir and its vicinity has been captured in the Autonomous 
Republic of Nakhichevan and another one in Aydin. According to 
a statement issued by the Igdir Governor's Office, during the 
interrogation of the terrorist who was captured by the 
authorities in Nakhichevan and handed over to Turkey,and the one 
captured in Aydin, it was determined that they martyred a 1st 
lieutenant and a policeman, injured four soldiers and killed 
three citizens. It was also determined that they were involved 
in many cases of arson in the region. A revolver and large 
amounts of ammunition were seized. 

