<H3> <TI>   Five Injured in Ferry Explosion </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Five Injured in Ferry Explosion </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1106132794 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network in Turkish 
1300 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1106132794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Five persons were slightly injured in an explosion 
aboard a passenger ferry in Istanbul's Eminonu Quay. According 
to a TRT correspondent, an explosion occurred aboard the 
Rumelikavagi at 1315 [1015 GMT] today, as it was preparing to 
leave Eminonu for Uskudar. Five citizens were slightly injured 
by the explosion in the stern of the boat. They were taken to 
Hasiki State Hospital for treatment. Hospital officials report 
that the injured are in good condition. Security officials said 
that the boat was taken by tug to open waters and that the 
investigation into the explosion is continuing. 

</TEXT>

