<H3> <TI>   Occhetto Comments </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Occhetto Comments </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1306141894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1343 GMT 
13 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1306141894 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>
<F P=105>  Italian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Achille Occhetto has resigned as secretary of the 
Democratic Party of the Left [PDS] in a letter to Giglia 
Tedesco, the chairman of the party's commission. 
  "I want to avoid groundless objections and controversy by 
submitting my resignation," Occhetto wrote. "My decision is not 
capitulation, but an act of pride and struggle in the name of 
the PDS and the Left." 

</TEXT>

