<H3> <TI>   PKK Members Captured in Izmir </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    PKK Members Captured in Izmir </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1406115794 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1406115794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seventeen members of the PKK [Workers Party of 
Kurdistan] terror organization who were involved in a murder 
case and various terrorist incidents have been captured in 
operations carried out in Izmir. According to information given 
by the Izmir Security Directorate's Antiterror Department, the 
suspects were involved in the murder of Mehmet Oztep in 
Karsiyaka, in throwing Molotov cocktails in various quarters of 
the city, and in hanging posters. Two revolvers, cartridges, 
medicine and medical equipment, and organizational documents 
have also been seized. The PKK's Karsiyaka regional official is 
among those captured. 

