<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Bomb Explodes on Istanbul Bus; No Injuries </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bomb Explodes on Istanbul Bus; No Injuries </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1406082894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 0700 
GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1406082894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] A bomb was placed on a city bus in Istanbul. 
The ticket collector aboard the bus noticed the package and 
threw it off. It exploded on the road. Nobody was hurt by the 
explosion. 
  According to information received from Istanbul Security 
Directorate officials, the incident happened at around 0800 on a 
double-decker city bus traveling from Taksim to Bostanci. Two 
suspicious-looking people, who got on the bus at Taksim, left 
the bomb on the upper level after the bus crossed the Strait 
Bridge. The ticket collector became suspicious and threw the 
package off the bus. It exploded on the highway. No damage 
occurred and no one was hurt by the explosion. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

