<F P=100> GERMANY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Results of 12 Jun Local Elections Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Results of 12 Jun Local Elections Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1506115994 </F>
<F P=103> LD1506115994 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
BFN 

    [Editorial Report] Berlin N-TV in German at 1000 GMT on 15 
June broadcasts a two-minute recorded report by an unidentified 
